{"text_id":160236,"tokens":["Hey"," there",","," fellow"," Red","ditor","!"," I"," totally"," understand"," your"," concern"," about"," phone"," and"," tech"," radiation",","," especially"," when"," it"," comes"," from"," your"," parents","."," I"," mean",","," who"," doesn","'","t"," trust"," their"," parents",","," right","?"," But"," let","'","s"," dive"," into"," the"," science"," behind"," it"," and"," separate"," fact"," from"," fiction",".","\n\n","Firstly",","," it","'","s"," true"," that"," phones"," and"," tech"," devices"," do"," emit"," a"," type"," of"," electromagnetic"," radiation",","," known"," as"," radio","frequency"," (","RF",")"," radiation","."," This"," is"," a"," form"," of"," non","-","ion","izing"," radiation",","," which"," is"," different"," from"," ionizing"," radiation"," like"," X","-","rays"," or"," gamma"," rays","."," RF"," radiation"," is"," used"," to"," transmit"," signals"," between"," devices",","," allowing"," you"," to"," make"," calls",","," send"," texts",","," and"," browse"," the"," internet",".","\n\n","Now",","," here","'","s"," the"," important"," part",":"," the"," intensity"," of"," RF"," radiation"," emitted"," by"," phones"," and"," tech"," devices"," is"," regulated"," by"," government"," agencies"," like"," the"," Federal"," Communications"," Commission"," (","FCC",")"," in"," the"," US","."," These"," agencies"," set"," safety"," limits"," for"," the"," amount"," of"," RF"," radiation"," that"," can"," be"," emitted"," by"," devices",","," and"," manufacturers"," must"," ensure"," their"," products"," comply"," with"," these"," limits",".","\n\n","Numerous"," scientific"," studies"," have"," investigated"," the"," potential"," health"," effects"," of"," RF"," radiation",","," and"," the"," consensus"," is"," that"," the"," current"," evidence"," does"," not"," suggest"," a"," link"," between"," phone"," use"," and"," increased"," risk"," of"," cancer"," or"," other"," health"," problems","."," The"," World"," He